{"tid":2270784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚得志涉高叫「黑警死全家」 被加控串謀發表煽動文字罪","createTime":"2020-11-04T08:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:32.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5d0070b4a1f33c93df339800281bc520f9e82f","tid":2270784,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"譚得志被加控串謀發表煽動文字罪 轉區院審理<br />\n<br />\n綽號「快必」的人民力量成員譚得志，涉嫌發表煽動文字和在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為的案件，上午在西九龍法院提訊，控方申請加控一項串謀發表煽動文字罪，將案件轉介區域法院審理，總裁判官蘇惠德批准控方申請，排期在本月17日再開庭處理，以便將案件與另外2宗同樣涉發表煽動文字的案件合併處理，被告須繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n新加的控罪指，48歲被告在今年7月在旺角西洋菜南街與亞皆老街一帶，與不知名人士串謀發表煽動文字。被告早前被指在多次擺街站時，涉高叫「黑警死全家」等口號，被控5項發表煽動文字和1項在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為罪。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2364685&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcysyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=ee914614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364685</a>"},{"pid":"5e9d949e2bb86e86ccf274274dda35cac661b949","tid":2270784,"uid":352936,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"黑警死全族"},{"pid":"e4371b9a6a08c7034e401c844aa1aceb6052d582","tid":2270784,"uid":370061,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"黑警全家不得好死"},{"pid":"c6c86191cad2dc80a381b4bccc98cc2d08f735c2","tid":2270784,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"恭喜你呀 香港文字獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297abcf286ce61b69d4ddba78de974a068f6304c","tid":2270784,"uid":92697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家呀屌你"},{"pid":"eae3250d1957b1a8bfb197dac97fa190af9838c2","tid":2270784,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"mon po狗見字冚家剷"},{"pid":"31562d8ed6a1c0dc0378137418958db0c14909c2","tid":2270784,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ffbd38a32f00781222c6583f6793150ac55f62","tid":2270784,"uid":79893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">警甴仆街冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p></strong>"},{"pid":"91c1e82fd14c699041898a1dadd195c12459ff70","tid":2270784,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黑警死全家</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d31b2162c82ac75310c7d4524d55fcff36c01508","tid":2270784,"uid":104406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n做黑警啲屋企人都會有不死身？<br />\n<br />\n陳述客觀事實姐"},{"pid":"377e89fd96dddcd2eb18a4de1e556980f7f6cd3d","tid":2270784,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"人始終會死<br />\n<br />\n客觀描述"},{"pid":"b591a2ede5534c8b1a0e421d11be34ed16840cc8","tid":2270784,"uid":299514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"黑警係咩意思？<br />\n每個字我都識，擺埋一齊我唔明咩意思喎。"}]}